{"title":"Model Explainability Quick Reference","html":"<h1 id=\"model-explainability-quick-reference\">Model Explainability Quick Reference</h1>\n<p>Quick reference for model explainability.</p>\n<h2 id=\"shap\">SHAP</h2>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">import</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> shap</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">explainer = shap.TreeExplainer(model)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">shap_values = explainer.shap_values(X_test)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">shap.summary_plot(shap_values, X_test)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"lime\">LIME</h2>\n<pre class=\"shiki dark-plus\" style=\"background-color:#1E1E1E;color:#D4D4D4\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">from</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> lime </span><span style=\"color:#C586C0\">import</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\"> lime_tabular</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">explainer = LimeTabularExplainer(X_train.values, </span><span style=\"color:#9CDCFE\">feature_names</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">=feature_names)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">explanation = explainer.explain_instance(X_test.iloc[</span><span style=\"color:#B5CEA8\">0</span><span style=\"color:#D4D4D4\">].values, model.predict_proba)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Try next:</strong> Explainability builds trust!</p>\n","source":"21-model-explainability/model-explainability-quick-reference.md","githubUrl":"https://github.com/NabidAlam/road-to-machine-learning/blob/main/21-model-explainability/model-explainability-quick-reference.md","module":"21-model-explainability","lessonId":"model-explainability-quick-reference","guideId":null,"type":"module"}